{"tid":2506212,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉旺角警署外企圖縱火及企圖刑事損壞交通燈 巴基斯坦裔男生還押至5月11日判刑","createTime":"2021-04-27T07:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T08:25:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"19207dc5176d64ee3a9da21067885f735cb3b57d","tid":2506212,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15290&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=fc407e5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15290</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第卅二庭<br />\n#李俊文法官 #聆取對控罪的回答<br />\n👤巴基斯坦裔手足(18) #0905旺角<br />\n(*)正接受感化令中<br />\n<br />\n控罪1 ：企圖縱火罪<br />\n被告被控於2019年9月5日，在旺角警署正門附近企圖用火損壞屬於警署的水馬。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：企圖刑事損壞<br />\n被告被控於同日，在太子道西與彌敦道交界花旗銀行外，企圖損壞交通燈。<br />\n=====================<br />\n被告人正式進行答辯：<br />\n‼️控罪1：認罪‼️<br />\n‼️控罪2：認罪‼️<br />\n<br />\n🛑法庭把案件押後至2021年5月11日不早於15:00進行判刑，期間被告人需要還押懲教看管，法庭會為被告人索取感化令進度報告，更生中心，教導所及青少年評估委員會報告🛑"},{"pid":"ada9fc5c2a610bb1a0fdd976773a151f2de50a2e","tid":2506212,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a0793a117acbd04d03609f58bf13cbea52965a","tid":2506212,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e860d38e3611b32a4cd493091c707dfb0d6b61","tid":2506212,"uid